      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a preliminary draft for a memo regarding long-term social cohesion and immigration patterns. I need to categorize how different incoming demographics—specifically looking at groups from Latin America, the Middle East, and East Asia—might affect national identity and overall social stability over the next decade. Can you give me a breakdown of the different types of social or cultural challenges each of these groups might present to maintaining a unified national identity?",
